snippet.title: SNEAKY TROUBLE MAKING PETS will be your LAUGH OF THE DAY! - The FUNNIEST PET VIDEOS
snippet.description:
Animals are sweet and cute but sometimes they can be really annoying. Owners can just cry but you will laugh! Just look how all these cats, dogs, horse, goat,... make mess, annoy people, break things, steal, jump in people and so on. So funny, isn't it? What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
